flawed_nl_solution:
Sabrina had 20 - 10 = <<20-10=10>>10 cookies left after giving 10 cookies to her brother.
Sabrina's mother gave her 10/2 = <<10/2=5.0>>5.0 cookies.
So, she had 10 + 5.0 = <<10+5.0=51.0>>51.0 cookies then.
She gave 51.0 x 2/3 = <<51.0*2/3=34.0>>34.0 cookies to her sister.
Therefore, she only has 51.0 - 34.0 = <<51.0-34.0=17.0>>17.0 cookies left.
